    • Method Detail

      • getStrategy

        RoutingStrategy.Router getStrategy(net.dempsy.config.ClusterId clusterId)
        Get the routing strategy associated with the downstream cluster denoted but clusterId. There should be no need to start() the Router that's returned. Since the RoutingStrategy.Factory is the manager for the RoutingStrategy.Routers, the caller should release the RoutingStrategy.Router when it's done.

      • typeId

        default void typeId(String typeId)
        This will be called from the RoutingStrategyManager to let the RoutingStrategy.Factory know what the typeId was that created it. The typeId can contain information useful to the RoutingStrategy.Factory. By default this method does nothing.
